OL,3,CJersey Gas Company to be charged
OL,4,Cfollowing Haut du Mont explosion
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FJersey Gas Company Ltd will appear at
OL,8,Fthe Magistrates Court on Friday 14
OL,9,FMarch to be charged following an
OL,10,Finvestigation into the Haut du Mont
OL,11,Fexplosion.
OL,13,FThe explosion on Pier Road in St
OL,14,FHelier killed ten people and destroyed
OL,15,Fa block of flats in the early hours of
OL,16,FSaturday 10 December 2022.
