OL,3,CJersey Gas Company to be charged
OL,4,Cfollowing Haut du Mont explosion
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe company - which also trades as
OL,8,FIsland Energy - is summonsed to answer
OL,9,Ftwo charges that are criminal offences
OL,10,Funder the Health Safety at Work
OL,11,F(Jersey) Law 1989.
OL,13,FThey include:
OL,15,FIt follows an investigation by
OL,16,FJersey's Health and Safety
OL,17,FInspectorate (HSI) - the island's only
OL,18,Findependent workplace health and
OL,19,Fsafety regulator.
