OL,3,CJersey Gas Company to be charged
OL,4,Cfollowing Haut du Mont explosion
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe HSI inquiry into the incident is
OL,8,Fpart of Operation Spire, running
OL,9,Falongside the States of Jersey
OL,10,FPolice's own investigation.
OL,12,FIn February, Neil Armstrong, 56, Lee
OL,13,FWard, 57, and John Wright, 59 were
OL,14,Fcharged with gross negligence
OL,15,Fmanslaughter.
OL,17,FAll three men worked for Island Energy
OL,18,Fat the time of the incident.
