OL,3,CJersey Gas Company to be charged
OL,4,Cfollowing Haut du Mont explosion
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FGraeme Millar, CEO of Islands Energy
OL,8,FGroup, has stated: "Our sympathies
OL,9,Fremain with the families who were
OL,10,Fimpacted by the tragedy at Haut du
OL,11,FMont.
OL,13,F"Safety remains Island Energy's top
OL,14,Fpriority.
OL,16,F"Given the ongoing legal proceedings,
OL,17,Fit would not be appropriate to comment
OL,18,Ffurther on the matter at this time."
OL,20,FThe victims' families have been
OL,21,Finformed.
